    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-f029039d-71a6-49c1-9c06-3f0c0c9e651b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f029039d-71a6-49c1-9c06-3f0c0c9e651b">
                Mr. Henderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f029039d-71a6-49c1-9c06-3f0c0c9e651b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-07-05/debates/a371b07c-4484-4b81-91fd-c369bcf276c7/SuggestedWorldConference#contribution-f029039d-71a6-49c1-9c06-3f0c0c9e651b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">In view of the fact that the international situation is steadily deteriorating, does not the Prime Minister consider this to be an urgent matter, and will he not approach President Roosevelt with a view to assembling such a world conference?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f029039d-71a6-49c1-9c06-3f0c0c9e651b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-07-05/debates/a371b07c-4484-4b81-91fd-c369bcf276c7/SuggestedWorldConference#contribution-f029039d-71a6-49c1-9c06-3f0c0c9e651b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-9f6584e3-04c3-4af8-8331-6d5e202b83ae">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-9f6584e3-04c3-4af8-8331-6d5e202b83ae">
